I have the fix direction: stop requiring pre-existing target cash, move funding to V2 flashswap, and use the reentrant victim borrow to finance only the flash fee via a second V2 pair. I’m replacing the verifier now so it keeps the original stale-accounting exploit path but uses a route that can execute from zero initial balances.
